			<p>Our cloud-based restaurant POS system was inspired by my work as a system administrator at Stem Hotel in Nakuru. It is a portfolio project for ALX Holberton Inco.</p>
			<p>The system allows restaurants to easily manage their orders, inventory, and sales. It is accessible from any device with an internet connection and can be customized to fit the unique needs of each restaurant. With our POS system, restaurant owners can streamline their operations and focus on providing great food and service to their customers.</p>
